data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. ESTATE SALE located in prestigious Sunset Park on a residential tree lined tranquil street yet walking distance to shops, restaurants , and local farmers market. This well maintained home boasts 2 bedrooms and 2 baths upstairs and half bath downstairs for guests. The dining room is centrally located with wet bar nook perfect for entertaining. Downstairs has front and back windows to allow light through out the home in addition can view the lush outdoor space bringing the outdoors into the indoors for more living area. In addition to spacious screened patio you will find a private back yard. The one car garage has it's own drive way for ample parking.
